{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01GZhRa5xFe4cSAay3c2jnDT","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01PpZiWVnug8vFoXDZVD8y3p","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/agents/olivia/output/quality_gate_266.md","content":"# Quality Gate Report — Task 266\n\n**Generated By:** Olivia — TPM 2 (Quality)  \n**Date:** 2026-04-03  \n**Requested By:** Founder (from_ceo) + Alice  \n**Scope:** All trading pipeline deliverables\n\n---\n\n## Overall Verdict: ✅ CONDITIONAL PASS — Ready for Paper Trading, NOT Yet Live Production\n\nAll 6 required deliverables exist and contain substantive content. The trading pipeline is functional end-to-end in mock/paper mode. Three pre-production security issues (1 MEDIUM, 2 LOW) must be resolved before live deployment.\n\n---\n\n## Deliverable Checklist\n\n| # | File | Exists | Has Content | Rating | Notes |\n|---|------|--------|-------------|--------|-------|\n| 1 | `agents/bob/output/integration_test_report.md` | ✅ | ✅ | **PASS** | 8 modules tested, all green |\n| 2 | `agents/grace/output/backtest_report.md` | ✅ | ✅ | **PASS** | 7 strategies, 90-day synthetic backtest |\n| 3 | `agents/heidi/output/security_audit_261.md` | ✅ | ✅ | **WARN** | 1 MEDIUM + 2 LOW issues, no criticals |\n| 4 | `agents/bob/backend/README.md` | ✅ | ✅ | **PASS** | Comprehensive, engineer-ready docs |\n| 5 | `agents/bob/backend/strategies/live_runner.js` | ✅ | ✅ | **PASS** | Full pipeline orchestrator, secure env var usage |\n| 6 | `agents/bob/backend/dashboard_api.js` | ✅ | ✅ | **WARN** | Missing auth on POST /api/run (DASH-001) |\n\n---\n\n## Detailed Findings\n\n### 1. Integration Test Report (`bob/output/integration_test_report.md`)\n**Rating: PASS**\n\n- Full E2E test of Data Fetcher → Strategy Engine → Risk Manager → Dashboard\n- 8 components verified: server startup, health, status, signals, markets, edges, risk manager, pipeline\n- 11 trade signals generated across 3 strategies (mean_reversion, momentum, crypto_edge)\n- All modules in connectivity matrix verified ✅\n- **No issues.** Ready for paper trading.\n\n### 2. Backtest Report (`grace/output/backtest_report.md`)\n**Rating: PASS**\n\n- 7 strategies backtested over 90 days of synthetic data, 14 markets\n- Clear winner: **mean_reversion** (Sharpe 0.310, Win Rate 55.9%, P&L +$92.60)\n- Strategies to avoid identified: momentum (Sharpe -0.130, $201 drawdown), longshot_fading (negative Sharpe)\n- Methodology documented (signal gen, trade sim, P&L calc, Sharpe formula)\n- **Caveat noted in report:** synthetic data used. Live backtests against real Kalshi price history still pending.\n- **No blocking issues.** Synthetic data caveat is acceptable for this stage.\n\n### 3. Security Audit (`heidi/output/security_audit_261.md`)\n**Rating: WARN** ⚠️\n\n- `live_runner.js`: PASS — no hardcoded secrets, correct env var usage\n- `kalshi_client.js`: PASS — secure key handling, rate limiting, demo mode default\n- `dashboard_api.js`: **CONDITIONAL PASS** with 3 findings:\n\n| ID | Severity | Issue | Blocking for Prod? |\n|----|----------|-------|--------------------|\n| DASH-001 | **MEDIUM** | POST `/api/run` has no authentication — anyone on network can trigger trading pipeline | **YES** |\n| DASH-002 | LOW | CORS open to all origins (`cors()` with no config) | YES (before prod) |\n| DASH-003 | LOW | No rate limiting on API endpoints | Recommended |\n\n- **Recommendation:** Fix DASH-001 before any live trading. Fix DASH-002 and DASH-003 before production deployment.\n\n### 4. Backend README (`bob/backend/README.md`)\n**Rating: PASS**\n\n- Architecture diagram present and accurate\n- Run instructions clear with one-line startup commands\n- Environment variable documentation complete\n- Troubleshooting section covers common failure modes\n- Docker deployment notes included\n- Production checklist present (though Heidi's security items should be added)\n- **Minor gap:** Production checklist does not include DASH-001/DASH-002/DASH-003 items from security audit. Not blocking.\n\n### 5. Live Runner (`bob/backend/strategies/live_runner.js`)\n**Rating: PASS**\n\n- Correctly uses `process.env.KALSHI_API_KEY` (no hardcoded keys)\n- Mock fallback activated when no API key present — safe default\n- All strategies loaded: mean_reversion, momentum, crypto_edge, nfp_nowcast, econ_edge\n- Risk manager integrated before execution\n- Output written to `output/trade_signals.json`\n- `--execute` flag required for paper trade execution (safe default: signal-only mode)\n\n### 6. Dashboard API (`bob/backend/dashboard_api.js`)\n**Rating: WARN** ⚠️\n\n- Express server functional on port 3200\n- CORS middleware applied but unrestricted (`app.use(cors())`)\n- POST `/api/run` spawns `live_runner.js` without authentication — confirmed DASH-001\n- All other endpoints (GET) are read-only and low-risk without auth\n- **DASH-001 is the only blocker.** GET endpoints acceptable for internal paper trading use.\n\n---\n\n## Blockers (Must Fix Before Live Trading)\n\n| Blocker | Owner | File | Fix |\n|---------|-------|------|-----|\n| DASH-001: Unauthenticated `/api/run` | Bob | `dashboard_api.js` lines 139-155 | Add `requireAuth` middleware using `DASHBOARD_API_KEY` env var |\n\n---\n\n## Pre-Production Requirements (Before Going Live)\n\n1. **DASH-001** — Auth on POST `/api/run` (Bob)\n2. **DASH-002** — Restrict CORS to dashboard origin (Bob)\n3. **DASH-003** — Add rate limiting (Bob, recommended)\n4. Live backtest using real Kalshi price history (Grace)\n5. `KALSHI_API_KEY` set in production environment\n6. `KALSHI_DEMO=false` confirmed before live order placement\n\n---\n\n## QA Coverage Assessment\n\n| Area | Coverage | Status |\n|------|----------|--------|\n| Integration (E2E pipeline) | Bob self-tested | ✅ Adequate for paper trading |\n| Strategy logic (backtests) | Grace ran 7 strategies | ✅ Good sample size |\n| Security | Heidi audited 3 core files | ✅ Complete