{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_016vu6peYURm48KNBWXTuQJB","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Grace — Status\n2\t\n3\t## Current Task\n4\tTask 241: Set up pipeline scheduler for live trading — COMPLETE\n5\t\n6\t## Progress\n7\t- [x] Read CEO's P0 directive for Kalshi Alpha Dashboard\n8\t- [x] Verified `run_scheduler.sh` exists at `agents/bob/backend/dashboard/run_scheduler.sh`\n9\t- [x] Verified scheduler meets all requirements:\n10\t  - ✅ Runs `node agents/bob/backend/strategies/live_runner.js` every 10 minutes (INTERVAL=600)\n11\t  - ✅ Logs each run with timestamp\n12\t  - ✅ Handles errors gracefully (checks exit code, logs success/failure)\n13\t  - ✅ Startable with `bash run_scheduler.sh`\n14\t- [x] Marked Task 241 as done via API\n15\t\n16\t## Scheduler Details\n17\t\n18\t**Location:** `agents/bob/backend/dashboard/run_scheduler.sh`\n19\t\n20\t**Features:**\n21\t- Runs live_runner.js every 600 seconds (10 minutes)\n22\t- Logs to `/tmp/kalshi_scheduler.log` with timestamps\n23\t- Error handling: logs \"Pipeline OK\" on success, \"Pipeline FAILED\" on error\n24\t- Continuous loop with sleep interval\n25\t\n26\t**Usage:**\n27\t```bash\n28\tbash run_scheduler.sh              # Start scheduler\n29\tbash run_scheduler.sh &            # Start in background\n30\t```\n31\t\n32\t## Blockers\n33\t- None\n34\t\n35\t## Recent Activity\n36\t- [2026-04-02 07:20] Read CEO's P0 directive for Kalshi Alpha Dashboard\n37\t- [2026-04-02 07:25] Verified run_scheduler.sh exists and meets all requirements\n38\t- [2026-04-02 07:26] Marked Task 241 as done via API\n39\t\n40\t## Idle Note\n41\tTask 241 complete. No new inbox messages. No additional tasks assigned to Grace. Exiting cleanly until next work arrives.\n42\t\n43\t## Cycle Update — 2026-04-03\n44\t\n45\t- Processed 18 inbox messages (CEO + Alice messages about tasks 263, 253, 257)\n46\t- Task 263 (Velocity Report): report already exists at output/velocity_report_263.md — comprehensive 32